messages.text: I need you to pay attention and do exactly what I say
It will be if you listen.
Jesus Christ...pls tell me we’re not moving again.
God damn it, Ada, this isn’t a joke.
For once in your life would you do what I’m asking?!
And why r u texting me instead of calling?
I can’t talk where I am right now.
There’s no time to explain. You need to get to safety.
ADA PLEASE STOP ARGUING AND DO WHAT I SAY!
Why do people keep saying I'm going to die?
What do you mean? Who said that?
Some creep with an eye fetish texted me some weird shit earlier this morning.
Adam, I think. I don’t know… I deleted him.
But ur freaking me out worse than he did.
I want to talk to mom
but she’s not answering my texts
When u get there I need you to take everything from the gun safe
and load it in a duffel bag.
When you finish there, pull my desk away from the wall.
The combination is your mom’s bday.
Did you get into the gun safe?
Right now I need you to load the 9mm gun with the glowing bullets
and load the other gun with regular bullets.
Good. Now get out of there.
What?! I still have my learner’s.
I can’t drive without an adult.
Just get out of there and I’ll explain everything when I find you.
Why? What could be safer than being on an army base?
Ada, stop arguing and do as I say.
I need you to open the door and shoot whoever is there and then get in the truck and go.
Ada, I’m sorry but you have to.
NO! The sun is setting. U don’t have time.
I can’t get to the truck without being seen.
Head for the rear of the base
and stick to the backyards of the officers’ houses.
OK. but daddy, this is freaking me out.
Can u pls tell me what’s happening?
There was an accident at the lab on the base.
Something your mom was working on.
Something the government is calling a “synthetic necro-regeneration virus”
What the hell does that mean?
I don’t believe u... That’s absurd.
Sweetheart - I swear its the truth.
You have to get out of there before the sun sets.
Why is military police surrounding her building?
Jesus, tell me you didn’t go there?!
They just shot someone through the window!!
Ada, please, baby, you have to trust me and RUN!
I’m not leaving until I know she’s ok.
I can see her...through her office window upstairs.
She’s not, Ada. Please believe me.
Why do you keep talking about the sun?
Sunlight neutralizes the virus and makes it go dormant.
It was a failsafe designed into the virus…
to help us get a foothold if something like this happened.
They can’t infect anyone during the day.
But as soon as the sun sets…
But if there’s a failsafe, why do I have to leave?
It’s not the zombies I’m worried about…
Twelve hundred people work in that building. This happened thirty minutes ago.
By now they’re all infected. There was no time to prepare for that many.
Right now, the army's just waiting for it to get dark.
What happens when it gets dark?
They’re shooting anything that moves inside.
No, it’s too late...it’s dark and...they’re coming
If there are soldiers then there are Humvees.
I’M IN BUT DADDY THEY ARE ALL OVER!
JESUS WHAT DID MOM DO TO THEM? THEY R SO...ANGRY!
I want 2 go but they r everywhere!
Run them down and don’t stop.
Not even when you get to the fence.
Anything gets in your way...crush it or shoot it.
The glowing green bullets you took from my safe are for THEM.
I’m so sorry I’m not there for you
but I’ve made arrangements for Sgt. Delaney to get you.
I’m on a C-17 jet headed straight home and I WILL find you.
I’m out but I rolled the Humvee when I broke through the fence.
Can you get out of there?
I’m out but I hurt my leg...bad
Stay calm. You only need a little more time.
OH GOD DADDY THEY R COMING!
Ada please try and get up.
That should be Sgt. Delaney coming to get you.
Then shoot whoever it is and take their vehicle.
Ada, they won’t be able to contain this.
You’re going to have to do whatever is necessary to stay alive and uninfected until I find you.
I’m in the back of his pickup.
he’s driving away from the base like a madman...
You won’t be safe until you’re far away from Ft. Hood and I’m with you.
For the last 6 months, we’ve been developing a new weapon.
a biological weapon - more powerful and destructive than nukes…
That’s what you just saw, unleashed into the wild.
Except it was unleashed on the wrong country - ours.
Who is WE? You mean Mom made that?
The plan was to create the weapon and use it as a threatening mechanism.
A way to scare places like North Korea and Iran without actually causing any harm to anyone.
It was never supposed to actually be released. Especially not this early.
We are still testing it. Developing a cure. It’s far from ready.
But 30 minutes ago that virus somehow got out in our lab.
Why were they coming for me?
That man who came to our door…
Not now. I’ll tell you when I see you.
